"*****************************************************************************
"" Abbreviations
"*****************************************************************************
"" no one is really happy until you have this shortcuts
cnoreabbrev W! w!
cnoreabbrev Q! q!
cnoreabbrev Qall! qall!
cnoreabbrev Wq wq
cnoreabbrev Wa wa
cnoreabbrev wQ wq
cnoreabbrev WQ wq
